Cell["\<\
It seems that ABC asymptotically approaches Phong as the value of \
\[Alpha]abc2 approaches infinity (here we also lacked an equivalence so we \
adjusted \[Alpha]abc1 values manually until the peaks matched).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5544965639826117`*^9, 3.5544965753276443`*^9}, {
